name: Kingspray Graffiti
summary: Create amazing street art with VR. Sharpen your skills or learn new styles with thousands of online artists from around the world. Up to 4 simultaneous players collaborating at once. Customize your in game avatar by designing your own hat, mask and spray can. Use True to life Ironlak Aerosol colours to design and develop skills and bring your concepts closer to reality.
